        <li>uses Bluetooth to connect your phone and glasses</li>
        <li>when your glasses are nearby and connected to your phone, the app tracks your glasses location with your phone's GPS</li>
        <li>you can see the current and last known location of your glasses on the map</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="panel">
